From 57e054e0f065656def7263a35eb2c2cfe0f6e180 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Jay Cornwall <jay.cornwall@amd.com>
Date: Wed, 25 Sep 2019 17:05:01 -0500
Subject: [PATCH 0685/4530] drm/amdkfd: Fix race in gfx10 context restore
 handler

Missing synchronization with VGPR restore leads to intermittent
VGPR trashing in the user shader.

Signed-off-by: Jay Cornwall <jay.cornwall@amd.com>
Reviewed-by: Yong Zhao <Yong.Zhao@amd.com>
Signed-off-by: Alex Deucher <alexander.deucher@amd.com>
---
